code: export default(function(){var posts=arguments.length>0&&arguments[0]!==undefined?arguments[0]:[];var action=arguments.length>1?arguments[1]:undefined;switch(action.type){case"FETCH_ALL":return action.payload;case"DELETE":return posts.filter(function(post){return post._id!==action.payload;});case"EDIT":return posts.map(function(post){return post._id===action.payload._id?action.payload:post;});default:return posts;}});
